					<p>Not many people see your content.</p>
				</li>
				<li class="p-12 pl-4 bg-white border-2 border-black rounded-lg shadow-solid -rotate-1">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-extrabold font-display">🗣️<br /> Engagement</h3>
					<p>It's hard to keep people interested and talking about your stuff.</p>
				</li>
				<li class="p-12 pl-4 bg-white border-2 border-black rounded-lg shadow-solid rotate-3">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-extrabold font-display">⏰<br /> Time</h3>
					<p>You don't have enough time to make new, good content often.</p>
				</li>
				<li class="p-12 pl-4 bg-white border-2 border-black rounded-lg shadow-solid -rotate-2">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-extrabold font-display">🤷‍♀️<br /> Resources</h3>
					<p>It's tough to use your money and resources right for making content.</p>
				</li>
