					<h3 class="text-lg font-extrabold font-display">😕<br /> Branding</h3>
					<p>It's hard to make your brand look the same everywhere.</p>
				</li>
				<li class="p-12 pl-4 bg-white border-2 border-black rounded-lg shadow-solid -rotate-1">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-extrabold font-display">🔎<br /> SEO</h3>
					<p>It's difficult to show up at the top of search results and get more visitors.</p>
				</li>
